The paper discusses the limitations of current 4G mobile networks and proposes solutions to improve disaster resilience and reduce dependencies between different entities. This topic is closely related to network infrastructure (cs.NI), network security (cs.CR), distributed computing (cs.DC), system and control (cs.SY), and architecture (cs.AR). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
